Room.Name: Golden Dolphin Way
Room.ShortDescription: You are walking along Golden Dolphin Way, west of Lankshire Parkway.
Room.LongDescription: You can see the intersection with Lankshire Parkway ahead to the east. The large Oceancrest Stables and Walking Yards are located on the north side of the road, and the looming City Walls surround the southern side of the road. Golden Dolphin Way continues to the east and west, literally from one end of the city to the other.
